content.detailedDescription: I was awoken in the night after midnight, i heard a voice that said,  look outside, i rolled over, i heard the voice again, it said, look outside, i went to the window, overlooking the sea was a huge orb of light. it was floating on the water coming from the west. i am on the oregon coast of the u.S.A. so it was coming from the west which would be asia. at first i thought japan was on fire by nuclear blast, but it did not go away. it hovered or floated for several minutes possibly 10 minutes, maybe more.  i was mesmerized by this orb of light that was "floating" in the water.   i knew it was not a boat.  it was just nw of buoy one. i could see the lights of buoy one and then to the right  was this huge orb of light.  as it floated the lights would move but the orb was still there. i finally "pooh poohed"  myself saying it must be a ship on fire in the horizon". so i layed back down & went into meditation .. i  asked what that was.. i was immediately told it was "ashtar"  and was told that he was "protecting us" , i immediately  got back up to go look again but they had left. i am of sound mind, i do not do drugs of any kind, nor do i drink alcohol.  this was not a "dream".
content.summary: i heard a voice it said to look outside. i saw a huge orb of light floating in the water! it was there for several minutes  possibly 15 minutes.. i went into meditation and was told it was ashtar protecting us!

content.detailedDescription:
On august 24th, 2016 at approximately 0600 hours, i was on my back porch smoking a cigarette. my porch is on the west side of the residence and it faces toward sturgis. i was looking at the sky to see if i could see anything strange which i do every morning. weather conditions where clear and dry, and there were only a hand full of stars out.
i was scanning the sky when off to the northwest i observed a large orb type object, white in color suddenly appear traveling westbound in a straight line direction. the object was glowing and traveled for approximately 5 seconds when the object expanded and vanished.
the object was approximately the size of a penny and when expanded it was  4 to 5 times it's size staying circular.   

this incident has boggled me because the reaction of the light. i have played the incident over and over in my mind. i then realized when the light expanded into a larger circle and vanished, the light had closed shut like the object had entered something.
content.summary: I observed an orb type object in the sky white in color westbound. a large white light surrounded the object and it disapeared.

content.detailedDescription: It happened when i was 8 years old.  i have a scar behind my right ear where they put the implant. i don't remember much except the bright light and laying on my side while they did something to my head.  the next day my dad asked me what happened to the corn behind our house and it was flattened.  although at the time i didn't know what happened i do now. i have lived an ordinary life but at times am able to do some amazing things which i wont even attempt to explain, but includes thought control and being able to hear what people are thinking at times. i know it sounds crazy, but its taken me over 50 years to be able to talk about it to anyone. i have never talked to anyone, but i do still want to remain anonymous. thanks.
content.summary: Iwas taken and somthing was put in my head over 50 years ago when i was a kid

content.detailedDescription: I decided to go out with some friends to bricktown, a hot spot for people to hang out on fridays/saturdays in okc. upon walking into one of the bars i noticed something strange in the sky in the distance. several orbs flying in all directions at incredible speeds (speeding up/slowing down). i have an extensive background in aviation as do all of my friends. none of us could explain what these were. keep in mind, there was a massive low pressure system which had just moved in with several huge thunderstorms. air was very turbulent and nobody was flying into will rogers world airport due to the conditions. these were not planes.
content.summary: Viewed series of orbs making incredible directional changes and changes in light intensities.

content.detailedDescription: My wife and i were eating breakfast we left the restaurant around 7:05 driving springville road she was the first to notice saying what the hell is that i look up there is a silvery discovering still making no noise lost sight of it in the trees and i made my turn onto my street i caught site of it again right as it started to move it started with tremendous speed behind a cloud i watched for another 5 to 10 min i never saw it again

content.detailedDescription: I was forced to leave my hunting camp near buzzard creek where myself and my friends had been archery hunting for elk, it was opening weekend. i have an old back injury from my time in the u.S. army and it had become very painfull because of the previous day of riding an atv in search of an elk.  i awoke at 2300hrs august 27th on my cot curled in a ball, sweating profusely, i had unbelievable pain in my back and abdomin. i layed on the cot a few hours waiting for it to pass but it only got worse. i'm a registered nurse and after considering that i may have a gall stone or twisted bowel, the pain made it difficult to function. i packed a few of my things and told my friends i was leaving and heading to the hospital, they all had their kids and families, so the only option was for me to drive myself. i was driving north on the silt cutoff towards i-70, which was approx 45 miles away on a remote and mostly dirt and mud road. the road crests near a location called mud hill, then it drops into a large valley filled with steep canyons and oak brush, the road zig zags down this steep section of road. i had gotten about half way down the zig zags and came out of a section where the road is covered with tall oaks and i saw this object about 300-400 yds away, hovering with multiple lights that almost looked like colored windows, while it was stationary, it appeared to slowly tilt in different directions. this is the second time in my life where i've had such an encounter, so i wasn't very nervous, but my pain was very severe and all i could think about was getting medical care. i stopped and watched the object for a minute or so and then wanted to make sure it wasnt a structure on the hill, it wasn't, it was free floating. i attempted to film it from inside the cab, but the ambient light from the dash wouldnt allow for zooming. i then stepped out of my truck and filmed it and was able to get 23 seconds of good footage. i couldnt stand the pain anymore than that and decided to continue to get help. the object remained there even after i drove away. i could see it in the rear view mirror as i was driving, i wanted to make sure it didn't follow me. i could have gotten much more footage had i stayed. i'm no stranger to this type of thing. i actively do bigfoot research and have had many terrifying encounters with them, so this was easy for me to deal with. i was just relieved that this time i got some footage and i have to say, it is quite impressive. as usual, the camera makes it appear furthur away than it actually was.  i could see it was a solid structure surrounded my flashing and changing lights. i do wish i hadnt been sick, i cant imagine what i would have filmed had i stayed.I will attempt to attach the video, but have had problems with that due to file size. if attachment fails, please call me and i will gladly get it to you somehow. thanks
content.summary: I saw the ufo hovering in a hidden valley near the road i was driving on, it was below the horizon.

content.detailedDescription: While washing my camper i was facing north looking at the top of the vehicle i noticed a strange object moving slowly across the sky. it was a very bright almost a chrome color it was just unusual to see it in a perfect blue sky background. i watched for about 10 seconds then turned to get my wife after i realized what i was looking at and that took about 5 seconds and it was gone. it was moving slow enough that  it could not have moved out of my line of sight, it was moving n to e about 12 degrees e from north. about 35 to 45 degrees from horizon. the shape is hard to describe it was taller then wide and i can't guess how far it was from me. no airplanes or clouds or vapor trails visible. whatever it was it did not belong in the sky.
content.summary: Observed silver or chrome colored object in north horizon moving strangely slow and it caught my attention and i watched for about 10 sec.

content.detailedDescription:
in early october of 1978 me and two friends went to the railroad bridge in the small town of high prairie alberta .In the early evening around 7pm with two cases of labatt's blue beer to drink .We sat down by a power pole at the edge of the riverbank 30 ft from by the bridge's eastern edge in the grass.We drank and joked around for awhile  i was getting concerned that they were getting too loud so i took a beer and went and sat on the bridge to keep six if any cops should show up.At this time i opened my 3rd beer and sipped on it.I
was looking towards the road bridge just north ahead of me about 300 ft or more .I was looking into the night sky.I was admiring the stars when all of a sudden in the top left front of my vision i seen a triangular shaped dark object that had a orange dome in the center of its underbelly flew past me and swooped down and around the river bend giving off a flash of white light heading in a southwesterly direction and was gone. this only took 2 or 3 secunds .If i wasn't looking in that direction when i was i would've missed it and saw nothing.I didn't hear a thing and it was fast and like in slow motion at the same time. i ran to my friends and asked them if they  saw anything just now and they said no probably because they were too busy horsing around and i didn't bother telling them what i saw or anybody else that night.Thinking back on it, i think  the ufo was following the river and mapping it for whatever reason i don't know. i mean what else it would be doing in a small town like h.P.? right.Well that's about it.I know nothing special happened but what the hell was it doing there in the first place just passing by hoping not to be seen by anyone following low above the river? well i believe in ufo's now after this experience that's for sure and if anyone don't believe me then they can take a hike because i know what i saw no-matter how briefly it was and i wasn't drunk either.I would like to send a drawing and photos ot the area i saw this thing at but don't know how at this time. thank you for reading my story. allen.
content.summary: I was having a beer on the railroad bridge at night and looking towards the road bridge facing north of me when all of a sudden...

content.detailedDescription:
I was driving south from hinckley to pine city, when an image of a "grey" appeared inside the front of my skull. his jumpsuit was silver, with orange trim. his eyes were large and black, and his skin a fleshy grey. it felt like i was being stabbed with pins, burning, and having my eyes torn open. i remember trying to pull the car over, but my hands couldn't move. the voice sounded almost feminine, though the lips didn't move, and went on for what seemed like hours, but i remember hearing "yes. become a grey, and the mysteries of the universe will unfold before you." my first reactions were screams of pain and terror, when i could finally open my mouth. i don't know how it happened, but it ended as quickly as it started.

afterwords however, it became clear that assimilation wasn't all they'd attempted. i knew that they were from proxima centauri, and that their planet was cloaked, yet these details were never mentioned by them.
content.summary: Attempted assimilation with motor control of target

content.detailedDescription: Sitting on deck just after returning from picking up dinner. talking with wife while seated facing north. i constantly watch traffic behind house and regular incoming flights to stl lambert international airport. suddenly noticed unusual green light between trees on horizon to the north, roughly the size of a bright star or venus. thought it was incoming aircraft landing lights but after watching for 3-5 seconds, realized it wasn't moving. so, i was curious as to what it was and continued watching. after another 2 seconds i witnessed the green light moved to the west slightly, opposite of normal path of incoming flights. i thought maybe it was a helicopter. still curious though, i kept watching and saw the light turn from green to red, then back to green, as if the object was rotating, while it was moving west from the original hovering position. as it returned to the green light, it dipped slightly on the horizon, then rose back to its original altitude, hovered for 1 second, then ascended a couple degrees. at this point i knew i was witnessing something very unusual and got chills. after ascending, the light moved west again about the length of your index finger held at arms length. without stopping, the light descended immediately from the westward direction and disappeared behind the tree line at the top of my subdivision. i waited 20 minutes for the object to reappear, but did not see anything again. based on helicopters and planes regularly seen in the area for last decade, i estimate distance of like-sized object with similar lights to be between 5-10 miles north of my location. if the object was larger, it was most certainly farther away and its movements much faster than normal craft. i am reporting this today to help corroborate any other witnesses since it happened on a friday evening near a major interstate interchange in sight of anyone traveling north on i-64 near i-70.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Green light just above tree line hovering in area of normal commercial flight path towards local airport. reversed path, hovered then descended behind tree line.

content.summary: Blue oval shaped came out of what looks like a portal

content.detailedDescription:
On this day, i drove into warsaw, mo. to check the mailbox at the post office downtown warsaw. as i was heading west , in front of newman`s grocery store  i passed a black car heading east with two men in it.
the men were dressed in black suits and black glasses riding in a older model black car. i thought right away, men-in-black! i thought that was an odd event. i picked up the mail and headed back to the office outside of warsaw south.
an hour later, i needed to run out to the warsaw high school for some paper work. as i headed on hwy south towards the high school, i just happened to look left down hwy mm and there sit the black car facing north towards our office. i thought how odd!
later that day, i finished work and headed home to sedalia, mo.
when i arrived to my apartment, around 6:30pm, i looked out my second floor apartment sliding door and saw the same black car backed into the apartment complex parking lot! i thought what heavens?
about an hour later, the car was gone. i went over to see my mom, who lived next door. while i was over there, i also went to see ann older lady friend who lived next to my mom.
my friend told me that some irs men had ask her some questions about me. now, i knew why they had been there.
content.summary: On this day, i saw (2) men in black three times . twice warsaw, mo. locations and 1 time sedalia, mo. location.

content.detailedDescription: I was outside my house, in antioch, tn, playing with my kids and the neighborhood kids. i've been checking the sky when it's clear due to seeing strange things recently (my daughters and i went to their school playground last week and stayed until it got dark. my oldest saw some lights in the sky and said momma what's that? i looked up and saw 3 bright white lights starting to separate from each other and go in 3 different directions. one moved straight up in the sky, another moved south east and another northwest. not a single one was blinking and they were moving much faster than the airplanes in the area. i couldn't tell if they made a noise as there were airplanes in the area that i could here, all of which had blinking red/green lights of course.) i noticed the object tonight coming from the sw and kept an eye on it because of the unusual brightness and triangular v shape. it was like it was made of a bright red light completely. it didn't look like there were multiple lights. i also noticed the orange-red trail was not lagging behind like planes in the area normally do. it stayed at a consistent distance the entire time i could see it. the object moved ne at a fairly high speed, faster than the planes in the area for sure. i thought it was a commercial plane at first, but quickly ruled that when it was not blinking and when it came directly overhead and i could see the odd trianglular v shape. not sure exactly what time the sunset was, but the trail could've been orange-red  colored due to the sunset. i watched the object until i couldn't see it anymore with my eyes only. i didn't have binoculars handy. 5 of us total witnessed it and are clueless as to what it could be! i tried googling it like i do with just about everything else i see (the 2 green fireballs i saw last year a week apart from each other were pretty crazy looking, but they're somewhat common as far as i could find in my googling them.) totally would've recorded if i had my phone outside with me!! i'm hoping someone else noticed it as well!!
content.summary: Bright red (lit up all over by one bright light) triangular/v-shaped object, no blinking lights, witnessed by group of 5 during daylight emitting orange-red short jet like trail

content.detailedDescription:
I have witnessed this particular type of occurrence approximately 25 times in the last 7 years.  it occurs most frequently in the month of september for some reason. on sunday the 4th 2016 i first noticed it at 7:53 pm and it ended at 8:00 pm.  there was scattered overcast on the 5 th and i didn,t see anything.  on the 6 th i noticed it at 7:45 pm and it ended at 7:51 pm.  on the 7 th i again noticed it at 7:43 pm and it ended at 7:46 pm. last night on the 8th it started at 7.35 pm and ended at 7:48 pm. as i stated above it burns like a white phosphorus military flare except i have never seen a military plane in the area when it occurs.  
additionally, when it terminates it breaks up in a shower of burning fragments falling downward and leaving a trail of smoke behind.  however, almost always one of the larger fragments stops after about 1000 to 1500 feet and remains stationary for 15 to 30 seconds.  last night there were 4 commercial airline planes transiting the area during the burn.  one was further south than the other 3 and may not have seen it, but 3 of them traveling due west, it would have been about 10 degrees to the north of their flight path. these sightings have taken place looking due west with the object at about 70 degrees above the horizon.  oddly enough that places them approximately over downtown ft worth.  i do not know what they are nor will i speculate on their origin. contact me at the above phone number or email address if you have further questions.
content.summary: Flare like object burning white hot, then breaking up and falling downward.

content.detailedDescription: As i headed west on hwy 50. i noticed two crafts hovering on both sides north and south of the highway. there was 3 cars in front of me and 1 behind me. the crafts made no noise. as they rose up they began to strobe brightly white lights, strobe, strobe, strobe.I was following the craft flying from the south across the highway to the north. i could never get a good look at the object, due to the bright lights strobing. by the time i had gotten to the first stop lights, out of town, i was blinded. i hobbled my way back home. for days, my eyesight was messed up and i could not handle any bright sunlight or the tv colors. at first, i thought it was a stealth bomber. i later found out that the stealth cannot hover, they are made for speed.
content.summary: Heading west on 50 hwy as i went down in the llow valley west of sedalia, i observed two crafts hoverinag both north and south.

content.detailedDescription: It was 7 pm. i had just left my sister`s house near dresden, mo. as i rounded a curve, i noticed a man pulled over working on his car. i stopped and ask him if he needed any help. he was working up under his car. he said he had thing under control. as we talked, i noticed a small red-orange orb flying over the corn field behind me on the north. i watched it heading west and wondered what it could be. i was going to tell the man what i was seeing but the orb was already gone. i never said anything to the man. i soon left the scene and never mentioned it to anyone for a long time.
content.summary: I observed the orb heading from east to the west flying over the cron field.

content.detailedDescription:
At approximately 11:30 pm, 9-8-2016 i was in my front yard and noticed a very bright light in the sky. initially assumed that it was a hovering helicopter, but came back outside several minutes later and observed the very bright light in exactly the same spot. i grabbed binoculars and continued to observe for approximately 1/2 hour before getting a second pair of binoculars with the ability to zoom. 

through binoculars, the object was bright yellow with a distinct shape. from my viewpoint in appeared as a straight line with a distinctly lighted circle in the center, with 2 "pods" visible at the left edge of the object. the object was motionless.

i called my county sheriff office.  they refused to respond. i continued  to watch and at approximately 1:00 am a neighbor pulled into his driveway. i pointed out the light and asked him to look at it through my binoculars. he confirmed my description. 

i continued to watch until close to 3:00 am before fatigue overcame me.  the object was still in exactly the same place the entire time. i took six photos. 

it was clearly a structured object. to be clear, my observation began on september 8 and concluded on september 9.
content.summary: Viewed hovering object for more than 3 hours.  neighbor observed as well, through binoculars.

content.detailedDescription: I was parked out near marshall junction, at an old air force building no longer used. i began to hear loud humming coming from off the telephone lines. i looked up to the west and saw an orange-red spherev slowly coming just above the telephone poles. i was shocked and surprised. as i stood there frozen, i watched the object slowly cruise right above me in my clear vision. the inside lit up as orange-red. it seemed to have no pilot inside. the glow lit up outside the object. it looked like the shape of a large bullet. after i watched it go by, i got into my car and drove away. it made no sound and i felt like it was observing me like a giant eye.
content.summary: As i was sitting out by an old air force building near marshall junction, i began to hear the telephone lines beginning to hum loudly.As i looked around i saw the object coming along the telephone lines heading east.

content.detailedDescription:
I was sitting out at blind pony reading a book under a shade tree. i was watching the people standing on the edge of the water fishing.They were in the south direction. as i watched, i noticed a large silver orb/sphere coming in from the east right in front of the people fishing.As i watched, the sphere dipped down skimming across the water.At that point, i could only see the top part of the sphere. it did this 2 times right in front of the people.The people acted as though they never saw the sphere in front of them.
after this, i took my blanket and book and headed back to my car. i left from that area.
content.summary: I was laying out under a tree reading a book. i looked to the south watching some people fishing at blind pony.As i watched, i saw a silver orb come in from the east and skim down along the water. at that point, i could only see the top half of the sphere

content.detailedDescription: as i was driving in a southeast direction on west friendly avenue, i notice what appeared to be a burning missile like object headed downwards from the sky. the color was blue-white in appearance resembling the glow from an acetylene torch. in its downward path, the object passed through a cloud formation. the sky was partly cloudy. the angle of my viewing was about 45 degrees from the horizon and it appeared to be about 10 miles in the distance. there was no trailing residue and i i did not observe any impact.  please advise me as to whether this was an incoming meteorite or something else.
content.summary: Missile-like object headed straight down from the sky.  the glowing blue-white color resembled a acetylene torch burning.  there was no trailing residue. i did not see a crash as the object headed in a downward path.

content.detailedDescription: When i turned off the lights to go to bed, i saw  flashing lights in the sky se of helena, mt.  they looked like airplane lights, but, unlike airplane lights, they moved erratically and did not follow a normal flight pattern.  my first thought was that a plane was in trouble.  i got out of bed and went to the window to see better, and noticed similar flashing lights farther to the south.  my partner also witnessed the lights.  to me, the lights looked fabricated/not a product of nature, but my partner wondered if they might be some sort of atmospheric phenomenon - like tiny sparks of lightening (although we listened for thunder but heard none and the sky was mostly clear).  the motion seemed to be mostly up and down with a little bit of side to side.The lights moved around and seemed to make very sharp "turns" but stayed in the same general area and did not get significantly closer, farther, higher, or lower during the time we watched them.  the lights were bright white with a blueish hue.  we watched for about 10 minutes.  i went to get my daughter so that she could see the lights, and when i returned about 2 minutes later, they were gone. i was made uneasy, almost frightened, by the lights because i they were so strange.
content.summary: Lights similar to aircraft lights flashed and changed direction erratically (up down and side to side) then disappeared

content.detailedDescription:
End august / beginning september in 1976, 1977 or 1978 i went for a walk with the dog. my first position was about n 49.572562 e 6.161799. as the luxembourg airport is not far away, i was habituated in airplanes (jets). so, the object approaching from west was firstly an airplane approaching the findel airport for me. i was awaiting the noise from the jetstraems. but, there were none. so i looked a second time and saw a cigar-like silver objekt with three aligned orange-pulsing round lights at the bottom. i stared at the objekt, while it continued it's route over my head, without any noise. this confounded and banned me. as the building in the east existed already, i precipated to have free sight. over the fields (where now are buildings) the objekt turned to bright white and changed direction abruptly towards sky. in an hight, that must correspond with a satellite-orbit, it changed direktion once again towards north.. very much faster than an aircraft (that i knew well). i never saw a thing like this before or after. i was at the age of 15 - 17. 
after the abrupt lift-off over the fields i run at home to show my mother the objekt - all time pursuiving it ... my mother saw the glowing globe in the sky - faster than a satellite.
content.summary: Thought airplane changed direction suddenly
